<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.3.3">
<l>vantanāḷvan teṉneñ ciṭaṅkoṇ ṭāṉmaṟṟōr neñcaṟi yāṉaṭi yēṉuṭaic</l>
<l>cintaiyāy vantuteṉ pularkkeṉ ṉaiccēr koṭāṉitu cikkeṉap peṟṟēṉ</l>
<l>kontulām poḻilcūḻ kuṭantait talaikkō viṉaikkuṭa māṭiya kūttaṉai</l>
<l>entaiyai yentaitan taitammā ṉaiyempi rāṉaiyet tālmaṟak kēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He took his place in my heart, coming the day [I] came [here];</l>
<l rend="indent">he does not know any other heart.</l>
<l>Coming as [by my] intentions, he will not give me over</l>
<l rend="indent">to the vile ones below; this I certainly earned!</l>
<l>How I would forget the king in Kuṭantai encircled by groves</l>
<l rend="indent">where [flower] clusters sway,</l>
<l>The player who danced with pots, my father,</l>
<l rend="indent">my father’s father’s lord, our lord?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
